Package: longview-go
Maintainer: Kostya Vasilyev <kmansoft@gmail.com>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.7-1)
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/kmansoft/longview-go
Description: A port of Linode Longview client to Go
 Original software: https://github.com/linode/longview
 .
 Features:
 .
  * A drop-in replacement for Linode Longview client
  * Supports monitoring of system metrics (network, disk, system info), Nginx, MySQL
  * Does not support (yet) Apache or apt-get updates
  * Does not support (yet) dm and md disk volumes

